00:26:14,870 --> 00:26:15,520
Mu Xuanling!

499
00:26:15,950 --> 00:26:16,590
Xie Xuechen!

500
00:26:16,670 --> 00:26:17,240
Mr. Xie!

501
00:26:20,150 --> 00:26:20,840
Fu Lansheng!

502
00:26:21,280 --> 00:26:21,910
