506
00:26:35,390 --> 00:26:35,870
Qiumin!

507
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:39,670
He's not Xie Xuechen.

508
00:26:40,320 --> 00:26:41,040
He's the Demon Lord.

509
00:26:42,950 --> 00:26:44,800
